      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry, not the specific VAD impeller design. Operating conditions cover only 40% of the required flow-speed space. Gap analysis acknowledges geometric dissimilarity but does not quantify its effect on NIH prediction bias. Achieved Gradation 2 — three below required."
    },
