      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified by turbulence-resolved reference data (LES or DNS) in the tip-clearance region; hemolysis constitutive model uncertainty bounded.",
      "rationale": "k-ω SST turbulence model selected without LES reference data for tip-clearance validation. Hemolysis power-law constitutive uncertainty is acknowledged in the UQ campaign but model form error is not separately bounded. Factor not assessed; epistemic gap at MRL 5."
