      "acceptanceCriteria": "All boundary condition inputs characterized with probability distributions from clinical measurements; inlet velocity profile from patient-specific data required.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profile assumed flat (plug flow); patient-specific data not available. Blood rheology parameters sampled from literature distributions in Monte Carlo campaign, but clinical measurement-based distributions not established. Factor not assessed at required level."
